ed electrolyte. Therefore, this work suggests the use of\nconcentrated glyme-based electrolytes, the fine tuning of the operative\nconditions, and the careful selection of active materials chemistry as\nsignificant steps to achieve practical and safe lithium-metal batteries.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 9 Jul 2021 13:55:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-10-27"}
