odimension-1 Furstenberg sets in $\\mathbb{R}^{d}$. As another corollary of\nour method, we obtain a $\\delta$-discretised sum-product estimate for\n$(\\delta,s)$-sets. Our bound improves on a previous estimate of Chen for every\n$\\tfrac{1}{2} < s < 1$, and also of Guth-Katz-Zahl for $s \\geq 0.5151$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 9 Jul 2021 14:58:30 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 1 Nov 2021 18:03:50 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 8 Jun 2022 12:57:32 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-06-09"}
